s' => '顯示','Visible' => '可見','When selecting child elements each element is normally eligible for selection once only.' => '當選擇子元素時，每個子元素通常都只能被選一次而已。','Whether a candidate\'s response that is beyond the maximum duration of the item should still be accepted.' => '考生的回應如果超出題目時限，項目是否還被接受。','Whether a candidate\'s response that is beyond the maximum duration of the section should still be accepted.' => '考生的回應如果超出區域時限，區域是否還被接受。','Whether a candidate\'s response that is beyond the maximum duration of the test part should still be accepted.' => '考生的回應如果超出部分時限，部分是否還被接受。','Whether a candidate\'s response that is beyond the maximum duration should still be accepted.' => '考生的回應如果超出時限，回應是否還被接受。','Who can view the rubric block during the delivery.' => '遞送時, 誰可以瀏覽指導語區塊。','With Replacement' => '跟取代','An error occured during the import' => '匯入時發生了錯誤','Assembly' => '集會','Assembly import' => '聚集匯入','Assigned test-takers' => '已被分配的考生','Assigned to' => '已分配給','Attempts' => '試的次數','Create a new delivery' => '建立一個新的輸送','Create a test' => '建立考試','Deliveries' => '遞送','Deliveries library' => '遞送書庫','Delivery is not assigned to any test-taker.' => '此輸送沒被分配給任何的考生。','Delivery saved' => '遞送已儲存','Excluded test-takers' => '被排除的考生','Manifest not found in assembly' => '清單中未發現集會','New delivery' => '新的遞送','No attempt has been started yet.' => '沒有已開始的考試。','No information available' => '沒資訊可提供','Prepare, publish deliveries sessions.' => '預備，發布遞送時域。','There are currently no tests available to publish.' => '現在沒有考試可以發布。','There is currently 1 attempt' => '考生已試了1次','Add All grades' => '加入所有的分數','Add All responses' => '加入所有的回應','Add Test Taker' => '加入考生','All collected variables' => '所有收集的可變數','Anonymise' => '匿名化','Class' => '類別','Delivery' => '遞送','Email:' => '電子郵件：','Export CSV File' => '匯出 CSV 檔案','Export Table' => '匯出表格','First Name:' => '名：','First submitted variables only' => '只要第一個提交的可變數','Grades' => '分數','Label:' => '標籤：','Last Name:' => '姓氏:','Last submitted variables only' => '只要最後提交的變數','Login:' 